Student Dashboard:
- Next lesson spotlight card with Join button
- Real spending data from payments table
- 4 stat cards: lessons done, upcoming, tutors used, total spent
- Cleaner mobile layout

Tutor Dashboard:
- New earnings tab with full payment history table
- Shows tutor share (85%), pending payout balance
- Per-payment payout status (paid/pending)
- How payouts work info card

Admin Dashboard:
- New Payouts tab showing money owed to each tutor
- Per-tutor breakdown with Mark Paid / Mark All Paid buttons
- Summary cards: pending payouts, already paid, platform fees, revenue
- Pending payout alert on overview tab
- Bookings tab now shows student name, tutor name, and hourly rate

